UPDATE 14 ðŸ¤–
Released on 20/3/2021 - This update is focused on convenient things and fixes, along with a load of new content.

New level cap: 1525
Disabled Christmas event.
New island:
Forgotten Island
Final Second Sea island before Third Sea is added (coming next update)
New fruit awakening:
Rumble
New fighting style:
Sharkman Kung Fu
New race (specializes against teamers):
Cyborg
V2 - 10% defense against melee, sword, and gun attacks. Additionally, 15% of received damage converts to Energy.
V3 - Defense increases to 80% against any attack. After 2.5 seconds, release an explosion equal to 40% of absorbed damage + 7.5% of your max health.
New swords:
Pole V2
Dragon Trident
Added a few new titles.
Blox Fruits Dealer Cousin officially added:
Instead of candies, it costs regular Money.
Price increases the higher your level is.
Same 2 hours cooldown between purchases.
Added Enhancement colors (second sea only):
Customize your Enhancement color.
Find the Master of Auras NPC to buy new colors, or buy them directly from the Colors Specialist with Robux.
Weapons like True Triple Katana now have a white helix by default.
Looks better on blocky bodies. Currently working on a better method for Rthro bodies.
Added Youtuber kill rewards:
Killing selected YouTubers will reward you with a special title (Second Sea only, different title per YouTuber).
Additionally, you will earn MoneyIcon.png 250,000 and FragmentIcon.png 2,500 (both seas, one-time reward), as long as the level difference isn't greater than 800.
Only a few YouTubers have been added for now. More will be added later on.
Added small benefits for Roblox Premium members.
Minor upgrade to Fast Mode:
Disables certain effects that may cause FPS drops, especially the ones on Dragon's moves.
Changes to the Legendary Sword Dealer:
Changed spawn rate from 4-6 hours to 3-5 hours.
Changed despawn time from 5 minutes to 15 minutes.
Increased max bounty/respect to 25M (doesn't increase PvP boost after 20M+).
Fixes:
Fixed scam messages in the first world.
Fixed the Aura effect not scaling correctly on Buddha and Rubber.
Fixed the fruits gifting menu not showing everyone on the server.
Reset the raid leaderboard and fixed the exploit to get on the top 100.
Dough:
Fixed the flinging bug with C and F.
Dark:
Fixed the bug where people got stuck using unawakened C.
Fixed awakened V not despawning sometimes.
Fixed the awakened C effect sometimes getting stuck during raids.
Chat notifications now also show as game notifications (this means Xbox players can now see factory raids).
Buffs:
Death Step
Reduced the requirement from 450 mastery to 400.
Buddha
Slightly buffed V hitbox.
True Triple Katana
Slightly reduced end lag on Z.
String awakening:
Buffed Z range, speed, and stunning.
Buffed X hitbox, stun and charge time.
Control:
Increased the stun on C.
Slightly increased the damage on V.
Nerfs:
Dragon
Nerfed defense from 70% to 62.5%.
Triple Dark Blade
Heavily nerfed.
Official lore update
